properties.Name: ConsentDocument
properties.Description:
A document associated with the consent. 

The associated document will outline the details of the consent that was provided. This can include details such as:
- permitted use of data
- how data will be used (including process)
- who will utilize data

Columns.Name: ConsentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Consent.

Columns.Name: DocumentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Document.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated data is effective or 'as-of'.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated data is effective or 'as-of'.

Columns.Name: ConsentDocumentNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Consent Document.
